OL,6,FIt was also revealed that Ian Rawle
OL,7,Fonce had his shotgun certificate
OL,8,Frevoked by the police, who said they
OL,9,Fwere concerned he was "easily moved to
OL,10,Fanger" and posed a "danger to public
OL,11,Fsafety".
OL,13,FChristine Rawle's son, Tom Rawle, told
OL,14,Fthe court he frequently witnessed his
OL,15,Fstep-father being violent, and was
OL,16,Fonce left with a 'severe burn' after
OL,17,Fhaving a hot ashtray thrown at him.
