OL,6,FTom, 38, said he remembers Ian Rawle -
OL,7,Fwhom he referred to as 'dad' -
OL,8,Fstamping on his toys, punching and
OL,9,Fkicking his mother, insulting family
OL,10,Fmembers and having regular arguments.
OL,12,FOn one occasion, when he was about ten
OL,13,Fyears old, Tom said he was injured by
OL,14,FIan Rawle.
OL,16,F"Dad and I were doing some homework,
OL,17,Fmaths I believe," Tom said.
