OL,6,FHe described other incidents in which
OL,7,FIan Rawle hit his mother with a riding
OL,8,Fcrop and "split her face open", and
OL,9,F"kicked her with steel-capped boots
OL,10,Fon".
OL,12,F'If timings were off with meal times,
OL,13,Fthat could cause arguments," Tom Rawle
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"Dad coming home from work, depending
OL,17,Fon what kind of day he'd had, that
OL,18,Fcould cause arguments. If mum hadn't
OL,19,Fdone duties around the house, that
OL,20,Fcould cause arguments.
