OL,6,F"He thought I was underachieving and
OL,7,Fthat I wasn't putting enough effort
OL,8,Finto life in the way he would have
OL,9,Fpreferred."
OL,11,FChristine Rawle denies murder and the
OL,12,Ftrial continues.
